<h4 id="index-revaluation" sourcefile="finance/asset-leasing/asset-leasing-quick-start.md" sourcestartlinenumber="181">Index revaluation</h4>
<p sourcefile="finance/asset-leasing/asset-leasing-quick-start.md" sourcestartlinenumber="182">This is the asset leasing account for variable lease payments measured by an index rate. Changes in lease payments caused by index rate fluctuations constitute a lease adjustment under IFRS 16. The lease liability and right-of-use assets will be adjusted to account for the new payments.</p>
